        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Welcome to Car Configurator</h2>
            <p>Car Configurator is an innovative platform that allows users to design and customize their dream cars. Whether you are a car enthusiast, a prospective buyer, or just love playing with car designs, our tool provides you with an intuitive and interactive experience.</p>
        </div>
