            <h2>Features</h2>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Extensive Customization Options</h3>
                <p>Choose from a variety of car models, colors, rims, and other accessories to build the perfect car for your needs and preferences.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>3D Visualization</h3>
                <p>Get a realistic 3D view of your customized car from different angles. Our advanced rendering technology ensures that every detail is accurately represented.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Share Your Designs</h3>
                <p>Share your customized car designs with friends and family via social media or email. Get feedback and make adjustments easily.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Save and Compare</h3>
                <p>Save your designs and compare different configurations to make the best decision before making a purchase.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
